# Do not edit files using Python scripts

When modifying files in this repository:

- Do not use `python`, `python3`, or inline Python scripts to read/modify/write project files.
- Prefer dedicated editing tools (`ApplyPatch`, direct file edit tools) for deterministic, reviewable changes.
- If scripting is truly necessary, ask the user first and explain why normal edit tools are insufficient.
